  32:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (#) Initialize the UART low level resources by implementing the HAL_UART_MspInit() API:
  33:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) Enable the USARTx interface clock.
