  34:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) UART pins configuration:
  35:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Enable the clock for the UART GPIOs.
  36:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Configure these UART pins as alternate function pull-up.
  37:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) NVIC configuration if you need to use interrupt process (HAL_UART_Transmit_IT()
  38:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****              and HAL_UART_Receive_IT() APIs):
  39:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Configure the USARTx interrupt priority.
  40:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Enable the NVIC USART IRQ handle.
  41:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) UART interrupts handling:
  42:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****               -@@-  The specific UART interrupts (Transmission complete interrupt,
  43:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****                 RXNE interrupt, RX/TX FIFOs related interrupts and Error Interrupts)
  44:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****                 are managed using the macros __HAL_UART_ENABLE_IT() and __HAL_UART_DISABLE_IT()
  45:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****                 inside the transmit and receive processes.
  46:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****         (++) DMA Configuration if you need to use DMA process (HAL_UART_Transmit_DMA()
  47:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****              and HAL_UART_Receive_DMA() APIs):
  48:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Declare a DMA handle structure for the Tx/Rx channel.
  49:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Enable the DMAx interface clock.
  50:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Configure the declared DMA handle structure with the required Tx/Rx parameters.
  51:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Configure the DMA Tx/Rx channel.
  52:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Associate the initialized DMA handle to the UART DMA Tx/Rx handle.
  53:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****             (+++) Configure the priority and enable the NVIC for the transfer complete
  54:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****                   interrupt on the DMA Tx/Rx channel.
