  91:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     Function HAL_UART_RegisterCallback() allows to register following callbacks:
  92:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) TxHalfCpltCallback        : Tx Half Complete Callback.
  93:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) TxCpltCallback            : Tx Complete Callback.
  94:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) RxHalfCpltCallback        : Rx Half Complete Callback.
  95:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) RxCpltCallback            : Rx Complete Callback.
  96:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) ErrorCallback             : Error Callback.
  97:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) AbortCpltCallback         : Abort Complete Callback.
  98:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) AbortTransmitCpltCallback : Abort Transmit Complete Callback.
  99:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) AbortReceiveCpltCallback  : Abort Receive Complete Callback.
 100:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) WakeupCallback            : Wakeup Callback.
 101:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) RxFifoFullCallback        : Rx Fifo Full Callback.
 102:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) TxFifoEmptyCallback       : Tx Fifo Empty Callback.
 103:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) MspInitCallback           : UART MspInit.
 104:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) MspDeInitCallback         : UART MspDeInit.
 105:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     This function takes as parameters the HAL peripheral handle, the Callback ID
 106:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     and a pointer to the user callback function.
 107:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c **** 
 108:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     [..]
 109:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     Use function HAL_UART_UnRegisterCallback() to reset a callback to the default
 110:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     weak function.
 111:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     HAL_UART_UnRegisterCallback() takes as parameters the HAL peripheral handle,
 112:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     and the Callback ID.
 113:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     This function allows to reset following callbacks:
 114:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) TxHalfCpltCallback        : Tx Half Complete Callback.
 115:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) TxCpltCallback            : Tx Complete Callback.
 116:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) RxHalfCpltCallback        : Rx Half Complete Callback.
 117:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) RxCpltCallback            : Rx Complete Callback.
 118:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) ErrorCallback             : Error Callback.
 119:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) AbortCpltCallback         : Abort Complete Callback.
 120:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) AbortTransmitCpltCallback : Abort Transmit Complete Callback.
 121:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) AbortReceiveCpltCallback  : Abort Receive Complete Callback.
