 123:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) RxFifoFullCallback        : Rx Fifo Full Callback.
 124:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) TxFifoEmptyCallback       : Tx Fifo Empty Callback.
 125:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     (+) MspInitCallback           : UART MspInit.
