 248:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     [..]
 249:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     This subsection provides a set of functions allowing to initialize the USARTx or the UARTy
