2827:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****     This subsection provides a set of functions allowing to control the UART.
2828:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****      (+) HAL_UART_ReceiverTimeout_Config() API allows to configure the receiver timeout value on th
2829:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****      (+) HAL_UART_EnableReceiverTimeout() API enables the receiver timeout feature
2830:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****      (+) HAL_UART_DisableReceiverTimeout() API disables the receiver timeout feature
2831:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****      (+) HAL_MultiProcessor_EnableMuteMode() API enables mute mode
2832:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****      (+) HAL_MultiProcessor_DisableMuteMode() API disables mute mode
2833:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****      (+) HAL_MultiProcessor_EnterMuteMode() API enters mute mode
2834:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****      (+) UART_SetConfig() API configures the UART peripheral
2835:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****      (+) UART_AdvFeatureConfig() API optionally configures the UART advanced features
2836:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****      (+) UART_CheckIdleState() API ensures that TEACK and/or REACK are set after initialization
2837:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****      (+) HAL_HalfDuplex_EnableTransmitter() API disables receiver and enables transmitter
2838:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****      (+) HAL_HalfDuplex_EnableReceiver() API disables transmitter and enables receiver
2839:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c ****      (+) HAL_LIN_SendBreak() API transmits the break characters
2840:Drivers/STM32WLxx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32wlxx_hal_uart.c **** @endverbatim
